  "description": "For registration requirements and regulations, please review here or contact Audrey Hanna | 518-625-8581 | ahanna@crexi.​com.​ Property tours are available on 6/9 & 6/18 by appointment only only.​ Please contact the listing broker to schedule a tour.​ Conference Center at 3326 Kimberly Road, Davenport, IA 52807 offers a compelling value-add opportunity in one of the Quad Cities’ most accessible commercial corridors.​ Positioned just off I-74 with immediate connectivity to I-80 and US Highway 6, the property benefits from strong visibility, convenient regional access, and proximity to Downtown Davenport, Moline, and Quad City International Airport.​ Built in 1995, the approximately 9,936 SF C-3 zoned asset sits on 0.78 acres and includes approximately 3,000 SF of conference space, 5,544 SF of warehouse area, one 12’ x 14’ overhead door, and a 1,242 SF open mezzanine.​ The conference component features multiple meeting rooms, an executive board room, and atrium space, creating flexible potential for event, office, industrial, or mixed-use applications.​ Surrounded by durable lodging, corporate, logistics, medical, sports tourism, and entertainment demand, this location is well positioned to capitalize on continued growth throughout the Davenport market.​ Nearby attractions and economic drivers include the expanding TBK Bank Sports Complex, major regional employers, and ongoing public and private investment across the Quad Cities.​ You also may be interested in the LaQuinta Inn & Suites (Parcel A): Click HERE ​ Non-Contingent ​ Earnest Money Deposit: Greater of $20,000 or 10% of the Purchase Price ​ Marketing Fee: 5% of the Winning Bid Amount, $20,000 minimum ​ $10,000 Participation Deposit 3326 E Kimberly Rd, Davenport, IA 52807",
